data.description: Rare floorplan in highly convenient location. Vaulted ceilings, formal dining, two living spaces & more make this house highly functional. Tile through entire first floor makes for easy care. Close to the mountains, Costco, other shopping, Manzano Mesa Multi-generational center, freeway, base, & labs. Updates include kitchen with Samsung appliances, granite counters, and custom accents. New windows, hot water heater, water softener, electrical, garage door are some of the other updates over the last few years. Backyard landscaped including a hot tub pad with electrical hookup, fire pit, pergola, and turf. Solar panels with Power Purchase Agreement keep utility costs down. Other features include primary on main with jetted tub plus a shower, &  dual sinks. Avail to move in June of 2024.
